- get pyenv : https://github.com/pyenv/pyenv
- install python by version: pyenv install 2.7.8/3.6.6
- $ pyenv virtualenv 3.7.1 (env-name)
- $ pyenv local (env-name)
- $ cat .python-version

##Start Django
- $pip install django

##Start app
- $python manage.py startapp polls
- create model
- add app to app install in settings
- register model to admin of polls
- $python manage.py makemigrations
- $python manage.py migration
- $python manage.py create supperuser

##Create new view in app:
-Create view in views
-Add urls

